"{\"uid\": \"egyptindependent.com-five-takeaways-from-the-opening-ceremony-of-the-2024-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"An opening ceremony unlike any other got the2024 edition of the Olympic Gamesofficially underway in Paris Friday night and truly it was one that will live on in Olympic legend - though maybe not in the way the Paris 2024 organizers would have hoped.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 100, \"end\": 105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6427899724895857e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 210, \"end\": 220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2270233123086556e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An opening ceremony\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 19}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024 edition\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 56}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Gamesofficially\", \"from\": 60, \"to\": 87}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic legend\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 175}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 205}, {\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are five takeaways from the opening of the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five takeaways\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 291}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris shows offIt wasn't exactly the night that Paris 2024 organizers would have hoped for (more on that in a moment).\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6427899724895857e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2270233123086556e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"offIt\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly the night\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the opportunity to put the City of Light and its culture and people on full display was well-taken on Friday.The boats floating on the River Seine allowed for incredible Parisian scenes as they passed storied landmarks on their journey to the end of the Parade of Nations at the Trocadero, with an Olympic-rings-adorned Eiffel Tower serving as the backdrop.\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"its culture\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 505}, {\"ngram\": \"full display\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"The boats\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"incredible Parisian scenes\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"storied landmarks\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"their journey\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"the Parade\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"Nations\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trocadero\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic-rings-adorned Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"the backdrop\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The famous landmark was lit up in all its glory, a veritable beacon on what could have been a dreary night.Much of the city was used as part of the performances, including videos of a torch-bearer running across the city's rooftops and through iconic Paris locations.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6427899724895857e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The famous landmark\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"all its glory\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"a veritable beacon\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 863}, {\"ngram\": \"a dreary night\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"the performances\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"a torch-bearer\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's rooftops\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the initial part of the ceremony flicked back and forth between recorded videos and live sweeping shots of the city, it really picked up when the focus was put on Paris itself.Parts of the city's history and culture were acknowledged throughout the ceremony, including a heavy metal performance in the Conciergerie with the windows full of headless Marie Antoinettes backlit in red, and a fashion show catwalk that went over the river itself.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6427899724895857e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1372, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3900795321656624e-44, \"text\": \"Conciergerie\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the initial part\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"recorded videos\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"sweeping shots\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"the focus\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"Parts\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1251}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's history\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"a heavy metal performance\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"the windows\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"headless Marie Antoinettes\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"red\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"a fashion show catwalk\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, and not to mention Lady Gaga performing a salute to the city's cabaret's culture on the banks of the river.As the sun went down, the City of Light shone through the raindrops.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1536, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a salute\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's cabaret's culture\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"the sun\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"the raindrops\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The running of the Olympic Torch passed down the lit-up Seine and around the magnificent scenery outside of the Louvre and the Eiffel Tower's light show looked incredible as it illuminated the clouds and rain with lasers and dancing beams.It was a strong preview of what the rest of the Games will look like with some of the city's most iconic landmarks serving as backgrounds for competition.The rain tries to steal the showThe rain had sent a warning Friday morning and threatened through much of Friday afternoon.\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3075399740128883e-37, \"text\": \"Olympic Torch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\"}, {\"begin\": 1749, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0042405952705265e-27, \"text\