": 4421}, {\"ngram\": \"stimuli\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4432}, {\"ngram\": \"sound\", \"from\": 4442, \"to\": 4447}, {\"ngram\": \"lights\", \"from\": 4452, \"to\": 4458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These spasms can be strong enough to fracture bone, and any fall can lead to severe injury, experts say.Stiff person syndrome is very rare.\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These spasms\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4472}, {\"ngram\": \"bone\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4510}, {\"ngram\": \"any fall\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4524}, {\"ngram\": \"severe injury\", \"from\": 4537, \"to\": 4550}, {\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4559}, {\"ngram\": \"Stiff person syndrome\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About 1 out of every 1 million people develop it and most general neurologists will see only one or two cases in their lifetimes.\", \"from\": 4600, \"to\": 4729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every 1 million people\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4637}, {\"ngram\": \"most general neurologists\", \"from\": 4653, \"to\": 4678}, {\"ngram\": \"only one or two cases\", \"from\": 4688, \"to\": 4709}, {\"ngram\": \"their lifetimes\", \"from\": 4713, \"to\": 4728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The condition can develop at any age and has been found to affect twice as many women as men.The exact cause of stiff person syndrome is not clear, but research has shown it may be due to an autoimmune response gone awry in the brain and spinal cord.\", \"from\": 4730, \"to\": 4980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The condition\", \"from\": 4730, \"to\": 4743}, {\"ngram\": \"any age\", \"from\": 4759, \"to\": 4766}, {\"ngram\": \"twice as many women\", \"from\": 4796, \"to\": 4815}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 4819, \"to\": 4822}, {\"ngram\": \"The exact cause\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4838}, {\"ngram\": \"stiff person syndrome\", \"from\": 4842, \"to\": 4863}, {\"ngram\": \"research\", \"from\": 4882, \"to\": 4890}, {\"ngram\": \"an autoimmune response\", \"from\": 4918, \"to\": 4940}, {\"ngram\": \"the brain\", \"from\": 4954, \"to\": 4963}, {\"ngram\": \"spinal cord\", \"from\": 4968, \"to\": 4979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pain relievers, anti-anxiety medications and muscle relaxers can be a part of treatment for this disease, and a new drug has recentlybeen fast-trackedfor development by the US Food and Drug Administration.Dion has been upbeat about her recovery, recently praising her doctor and saying that her fear of her conditionhas been replaced with hope.Her performance of \\\"L'Hymne \\u00e0 l'amour\\\" closed the ceremony in stunning fashion.\", \"from\": 4981, \"to\": 5404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5154, \"end\": 5156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9977532528038451, \"rank\": 0.001992278002869299, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pain relievers\", \"from\": 4981, \"to\": 4995}, {\"ngram\": \"anti-anxiety medications\", \"from\": 4997, \"to\": 5021}, {\"ngram\": \"muscle relaxers\", \"from\": 5026, \"to\": 5041}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 5049, \"to\": 5055}, {\"ngram\": \"treatment\", \"from\": 5059, \"to\": 5068}, {\"ngram\": \"this disease\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5085}, {\"ngram\": \"a new drug\", \"from\": 5091, \"to\": 5101}, {\"ngram\": \"fast-trackedfor development\", \"from\": 5119, \"to\": 5146}, {\"ngram\": \"Dion\", \"from\": 5186, \"to\": 5190}, {\"ngram\": \"her recovery\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5225}, {\"ngram\": \"her doctor\", \"from\": 5245, \"to\": 5255}, {\"ngram\": \"her fear\", \"from\": 5272, \"to\": 5280}, {\"ngram\": \"her conditionhas\", \"from\": 5284, \"to\": 5300}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 5320, \"to\": 5324}, {\"ngram\": \"Her performance\", \"from\": 5325, \"to\": 5340}, {\"ngram\": \"L'Hymne \\u00e0 l'amour\", \"from\": 5345, \"to\": 5362}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 5371, \"to\": 5383}, {\"ngram\": \"stunning fashion\", \"from\": 5387, \"to\": 5403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clad in magnificent white, Dion's performance drew goosebumps as she rolled back the years and her incredible voiced echoed along the Seine.A massive roar greeted the end of her performance from the spectators who braved the rain throughout the night as the Eiffel Tower sparkled around her - truly a moment worthy of a singing icon.A Paris party on a Friday nightA long dance break in the middle of the show encapsulated the vibe that much of the show took on: It was party time in the French capital.Plenty of techno and Europop music accompanied by colorful dancers wearing all sorts of rave outfits - including one singer fully painted blue singing on a bed of flowers - turned heads around the world as the French displayed their party scene.Earlier in the ceremony, the first moment that made people stop and stare was a performance by heavy metal band Gojira and their aforementioned headless Marie Antoinettes.\", \"from\": 5405, \"to\": 6323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5740, \"end\": 5745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6427899724895857e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 5892, \"end\": 5898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.995627196579294, \"rank\": 0.004362184483222859, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 6117, \"end\": 6123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.995627196579294, \"rank\": 0.004362184483222859, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"