\"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8738, \"end\": 8749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The boats\", \"from\": 8712, \"to\": 8721}, {\"ngram\": \"incredible Parisian scenes\", \"from\": 8762, \"to\": 8788}, {\"ngram\": \"storied landmarks\", \"from\": 8804, \"to\": 8821}, {\"ngram\": \"their journey\", \"from\": 8825, \"to\": 8838}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 8842, \"to\": 8849}, {\"ngram\": \"the Parade\", \"from\": 8853, \"to\": 8863}, {\"ngram\": \"Nations\", \"from\": 8867, \"to\": 8874}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trocadero\", \"from\": 8878, \"to\": 8891}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic-rings-adorned Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 8898, \"to\": 8935}, {\"ngram\": \"the backdrop\", \"from\": 8947, \"to\": 8959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The famous landmark was lit up in all its glory, a veritable beacon on what could have been a dreary night.\", \"from\": 8961, \"to\": 9068, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The famous landmark\", \"from\": 8961, \"to\": 8980}, {\"ngram\": \"all its glory\", \"from\": 8995, \"to\": 9008}, {\"ngram\": \"a veritable beacon\", \"from\": 9010, \"to\": 9028}, {\"ngram\": \"a dreary night\", \"from\": 9053, \"to\": 9067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Much of the city was used as part of the performances, including videos of a torch-bearer running across the city's rooftops and through iconic Paris locations.\", \"from\": 9070, \"to\": 9230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9214, \"end\": 9219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6427899724895857e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 9078, \"to\": 9086}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 9099, \"to\": 9103}, {\"ngram\": \"the performances\", \"from\": 9107, \"to\": 9123}, {\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 9135, \"to\": 9141}, {\"ngram\": \"a torch-bearer\", \"from\": 9145, \"to\": 9159}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's rooftops\", \"from\": 9175, \"to\": 9194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the initial part of the ceremony flicked back and forth between recorded videos and live sweeping shots of the city, it really picked up when the focus was put on Paris itself.\", \"from\": 9231, \"to\": 9413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9400, \"end\": 9405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6427899724895857e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the initial part\", \"from\": 9237, \"to\": 9253}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 9257, \"to\": 9269}, {\"ngram\": \"recorded videos\", \"from\": 9301, \"to\": 9316}, {\"ngram\": \"sweeping shots\", \"from\": 9326, \"to\": 9340}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 9344, \"to\": 9352}, {\"ngram\": \"the focus\", \"from\": 9379, \"to\": 9388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parts of the city's history and culture were acknowledged throughout the ceremony, including a heavy metal performance in the Conciergerie with the windows full of headless Marie Antoinettes backlit in red, and a fashion show catwalk that went over the river itself.\", \"from\": 9415, \"to\": 9681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9541, \"end\": 9553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3900795321656624e-44, \"text\": \"Conciergerie\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parts\", \"from\": 9415, \"to\": 9420}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's history\", \"from\": 9424, \"to\": 9442}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 9447, \"to\": 9454}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 9484, \"to\": 9496}, {\"ngram\": \"a heavy metal performance\", \"from\": 9508, \"to\": 9533}, {\"ngram\": \"the windows\", \"from\": 9559, \"to\": 9570}, {\"ngram\": \"headless Marie Antoinettes\", \"from\": 9579, \"to\": 9605}, {\"ngram\": \"red\", \"from\": 9617, \"to\": 9620}, {\"ngram\": \"a fashion show catwalk\", \"from\": 9626, \"to\": 9648}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 9664, \"to\": 9673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, and not to mention Lady Gaga performing a salute to the city's cabaret's culture on the banks of the river.\", \"from\": 9682, \"to\": 9793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9705, \"end\": 9714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a salute\", \"from\": 9726, \"to\": 9734}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's cabaret's culture\", \"from\": 9738, \"to\": 9766}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 9770, \"to\": 9779}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 9783, \"to\": 9792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the sun went down, the City of Light shone through the raindrops.\", \"from\": 9795, \"to\": 9863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sun\", \"from\": 9798, \"to\": 9805}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 9817, \"to\": 9825}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 9829, \"to\": 9834}, {\"ngram\": \"the raindrops\", \"from\": 9849, \"to\": 9862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The running of the Olympic Torch passed down the lit-up Seine and around the magnificent scenery outside of the Louvre and the Eiffel Tower's light show looked incredible as it illuminated the clouds and rain with lasers and dancing beams.\", \"from\": 9864, \"to\": 10103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9883, \"end\": 9896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3075399740128883e-37, \"text\": \"Olympic Torch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_flame\"}, {\"begin\": 9920, \"end\": 9925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0042405952705265e-27, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 9976, \"end\": 9982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"score\": 0.9999999603724071, \"rank\": 3.96278482416031e-08, \"text\": \"Louvre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The running\", \"from\": 9864, \"to\": 9875}, {\"ngram\": \"the magnificent scenery\", \"from\": 9937, \"to\": 9960}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower's light show\", \"from\": 9987, \"to\": 10016}, {\"ngram\": \"the clouds\", \"from\": 10053, \"to\": 10063}, {\"ngram\": \"lasers\", \"from\": 10078, \"to\": 10084}, {\"ngram\": \"dancing beams\", \"from\": 10089, \"to\": 10102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a strong preview of what the rest of the Games will look like with some of the city's most iconic landmarks serving as backgrounds for competition.\", \"from\": 10105, \"to\": 10259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a strong preview\", \"from\": 10112, \"to\": 10128}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 10137, \"to\": 10145}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 10149, \"to\": 10158}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's most iconic landmarks\", \"from\": 10187, \"to\": 10219}, {\"ngram\": \"backgrounds\", \"from\": 10231, \"to\": 10242}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 10247, \"to\": 10258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rain had sent a warning Friday morning and threatened through much of Friday afternoon.\", \"from\": 10261, \"to\": 10352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rain\", \"from\": 10261, \"to\": 10269}, {\"ngram\": \"a warning\", \"from\": 10279, \"to\": 10288}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday afternoon\", \"from\": 10335, \"to\": 10351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Paris' gray skies finally opened up about 30 minutes into a three-and-a-half-hour show, leading to perhaps the most drenched opening ceremony in the history of the modern Olympics.\", \"from\": 10353, \"to\": 10537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10357, \"end\": 10362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6427899724895857e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 30 minutes\", \"from\": 10393, \"to\": 10409}, {\"ngram\": \"a three-and-a-half-hour show\", \"from\": 10415, \"to\": 10443}, {\"ngram\": \"perhaps the most drenched opening ceremony\", \"from\": 10456, \"to\": 10498}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 10502, \"to\": 10513}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern Olympics\", \"from\": 10517, \"to\": 10536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hundreds of thousands of spectators lined the banks of the River Seine, clad in ponchos and rain jackets, and a canopy of umbrellas sprouted up at the first hint of raindrops.\", \"from\": 10539, \"to\": 10714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10598, \"end\": 10609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hundreds of thousands\", \"from\": 10539, \"to\": 10560}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 10564, \"to\": 10574}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 10581, \"to\": 10590}, {\"ngram\": \"ponchos\", \"from\": 10619, \"to\": 10626}, {\"ngram\": \"rain jackets\", \"from\": 10631, \"to\": 10643}, {\"ngram\": \"a canopy\", \"from\": 10649, \"to\": 10657}, {\"ngram\": \"umbrellas\", \"from\": 10661, \"to\": 10670}, {\"ngram\": \"the first hint\", \"from\": 10686, \"to\": 10700}, {\"ngram\": \"raindrops\", \"from\": 10704, \"to\": 10713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after about an hour of the wet stuff coming down in earnest, it was clear some of the crowd had had enough.\", \"from\": 10715, \"to\": 10826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about an hour\", \"from\": 10725, \"to\": 10738}, {\"ngram\": \"the wet stuff\", \"from\": 10742, \"to\": 10755}, {\"ngram\": \"earnest\", \"from\": 10771, \"to\": 10778}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 10801, \"to\": 10810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the grandstands at the end of the Parade of Nations, exposed onlookers ran for the comfort of hospitality tents and other nearby covered areas while cameras caught the occasional thinning of the crowd along the riverside.\", \"from\": 10827, \"to\": 11051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the grandstands\", \"from\": 10830, \"to\": 10845}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 10849, \"to\": 10856}, {\"ngram\": \"the Parade\", \"from\": 10860, \"to\": 10870}, {\"ngram\": \"Nations\", \"from\": 10874, \"to\": 10881}, {\"ngram\": \"the comfort\", \"from\": 10909, \"to\": 10920}, {\"ngram\": \"hospitality tents\", \"from\": 10924, \"to\": 10941}, {\"ngram\": \"other nearby covered areas\", \"from\": 10946, \"to\": 10972}, {\"ngram\": \"cameras\", \"from\": 10979, \"to\": 10986}, {\"ngram\": \"the occasional thinning\", \"from\": 10994, \"to\": 11017}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 11021, \"to\": 11030}, {\"ngram\": \"the riverside\", \"from\": 11037, \"to\": 11050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Franck Fife/Pool/AP The rain was evident in the performances as dancers occasionally took tentative movements or were seen having slight slips as they performed.\", \"from\": 11053, \"to\": 11215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Franck Fife/Pool/AP\", \"from\": 11053, \"to\": 11072}, {\"ngram\": \"The rain\", \"from\": 11073, \"to\": 11081}, {\"ngram\": \"the performances\", \"from\": 11097, \"to\": 11113}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 11117, \"to\": 11124}, {\"ngram\": \"tentative movements\", \"from\": 11143, \"to\": 11162}, {\"ngram\": \"slight slips\", \"from\": 11183, \"to\": 11195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The water sprung off musicians' instruments as they played and some of the boats carrying the smaller athletic delegations appeared tossed in the Seine's waves.\", \"from\": 11216, \"to\": 11376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11362, \"end\": 11367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0042405952705265e-27, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The water\", \"from\": 11216, \"to\": 11225}, {\"ngram\": \"musicians' instruments\", \"from\": 11237, \"to\": 11259}, {\"ngram\": \"the boats\", \"from\": 11287, \"to\": 11296}, {\"ngram\": \"the smaller athletic delegations\", \"from\": 11306, \"to\": 11338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Olympic spirit did not wilt in the rain.\", \"from\": 11378, \"to\": 11426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 11382, \"to\": 11400}, {\"ngram\": \"the rain\", \"from\": 11417, \"to\": 11425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes - standing in pouring rain days before they are about to compete in the most important competitions of their lives - looked beyond excited to wave to the crowds and France truly seemed to embrace the Games, though maybe most of the Parisians who did not had already left the city to flee the millions of people coming to watch the competitions.\", \"from\": 11427, \"to\": 11784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11605, \"end\": 11611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.063879386080735e-12, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 11427, \"to\": 11439}, {\"ngram\": \"rain days\", \"from\": 11462, \"to\": 11471}, {\"ngram\": \"the most important competitions\", \"from\": 11508, \"to\": 11539}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 11543, \"to\": 11554}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 11590, \"to\": 11600}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 11636, \"to\": 11645}, {\"ngram\": \"the Parisians\", \"from\": 11668, \"to\": 11681}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 11711, \"to\": 11719}, {\"ngram\": \"the millions\", \"from\": 11728, \"to\": 11740}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 11744, \"to\": 11750}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 11767, \"to\": 11783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Handout/Screengrab by IOC/Getty Images After a stunning light show on the Eiffel Tower, one of the most iconic singers of the last several decades finally made her return to performing after four years.\", \"from\": 11786, \"to\": 11989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Handout/Screengrab\", \"from\": 11786, \"to\": 11804}, {\"ngram\": \"IOC/Getty Images\", \"from\": 11808, \"to\": 11824}, {\"ngram\": \"a stunning light show\", \"from\": 11831, \"to\": 11852}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 11856, \"to\": 11872}, {\"ngram\": \"the most iconic singers\", \"from\": 11881, \"to\": 11904}, {\"ngram\": \"the last several decades\", \"from\": 11908, \"to\": 11932}, {\"ngram\": \"four years\", \"from\": 11977, \"to\": 11987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Celine Dionhas has been battling stiff person syndrome, a rare neurological condition that causes spasms, muscle rigidity, and a heightened sensitivity to stimuli, such as sound and lights.\", \"from\": 11991, \"to\": 12180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Celine Dionhas\", \"from\": 11991, \"to\": 12005}, {\"ngram\": \"stiff person syndrome\", \"from\": 12024, \"to\": 12045}, {\"ngram\": \"a rare neurological condition\", \"from\": 12047, \"to\": 12076}, {\"ngram\": \"spasms\", \"from\": 12089, \"to\": 12095}, {\"ngram\": \"muscle rigidity\", \"from\": 12097, \"to\": 12112}, {\"ngram\": \"a heightened sensitivity\", \"from\": 12118, \"to\": 12142}, {\"ngram\": \"stimuli\", \"from\": 12146, \"to\": 12153}, {\"ngram\": \"sound\", \"from\": 12163, \"to\": 12168}, {\"ngram\": \"lights\", \"from\": 12173, \"to\": 12179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These spasms can be strong enough to fracture bone, and any fall can lead to severe injury, experts say.\", \"from\": 12181, \"to\": 12285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These spasms\", \"from\": 12181, \"to\": 12193}, {\"ngram\": \"bone\", \"from\": 12227, \"to\": 12231}, {\"ngram\": \"any fall\", \"from\": 12237, \"to\": 12245}, {\"ngram\": \"severe injury\", \"from\": 12258, \"to\": 12271}, {\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 12273, \"to\": 12280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stiff person syndrome is very rare.\", \"from\": 12287, \"to\": 12322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stiff person syndrome\", \"from\": 12287, \"to\": 12308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About 1 out of every 1 million people develop it and most general neurologists will see only one or two cases in their lifetimes.\", \"from\": 12323, \"to\": 12452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every 1 million people\", \"from\": 12338, \"to\": 12360}, {\"ngram\": \"most general neurologists\", \"from\": 12376, \"to\": 12401}, {\"ngram\": \"only one or two cases\", \"from\": 12411, \"to\": 12432}, {\"ngram\": \"their lifetimes\", \"from\": 12436, \"to\": 12451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The condition can develop at any age and has been found to affect twice as many women as men.\", \"from\": 12453, \"to\": 12546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The condition\", \"from\": 12453, \"to\": 12466}, {\"ngram\": \"any age\", \"from\": 12482, \"to\": 12489}, {\"ngram\": \"twice as many women\", \"from\": 12519, \"to\": 12538}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 12542, \"to\": 12545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The exact cause of stiff person syndrome is not clear, but research has shown it may be due to an autoimmune response gone awry in the brain and spinal cord.\", \"from\": 12548, \"to\": 12705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The exact cause\", \"from\": 12548, \"to\": 12563}, {\"ngram\": \"stiff person syndrome\", \"from\": 12567, \"to\": 12588}, {\"ngram\": \"research\", \"from\": 12607, \"to\": 12615}, {\"ngram\": \"an autoimmune response\", \"from\": 12643, \"to\": 12665}, {\"ngram\": \"the brain\", \"from\": 12679, \"to\": 12688}, {\"ngram\": \"spinal cord\", \"from\": 12693, \"to\": 12704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pain relievers, anti-anxiety medications and muscle relaxers can be a part of treatment for this disease, and a new drug has recentlybeen fast-trackedfor development by the US Food and Drug Administration.\", \"from\": 12706, \"to\": 12911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12879, \"end\": 12881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9977532528038451, \"rank\": 0.001992278002869299, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pain relievers\", \"from\": 12706, \"to\": 12720}, {\"ngram\": \"anti-anxiety medications\", \"from\": 12722, \"to\": 12746}, {\"ngram\": \"muscle relaxers\", \"from\": 12751, \"to\": 12766}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 12774, \"to\": 12780}, {\"ngram\": \"treatment\", \"from\": 12784, \"to\": 12793}, {\"ngram\": \"this disease\", \"from\": 12798, \"to\": 12810}, {\"ngram\": \"a new drug\", \"from\": 12816, \"to\": 12826}, {\"ngram\": \"fast-trackedfor development\", \"from\": 12844, \"to\": 12871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion has been upbeat about her recovery, recently praising her doctor and saying that her fear of her conditionhas been replaced with hope.\", \"from\": 12913, \"to\": 13052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dion\", \"from\": 12913, \"to\": 12917}, {\"ngram\": \"her recovery\", \"from\": 12940, \"to\": 12952}, {\"ngram\": \"her doctor\", \"from\": 12972, \"to\": 12982}, {\"ngram\": \"her fear\", \"from\": 12999, \"to\": 13007}, {\"ngram\": \"her conditionhas\", \"from\": 13011, \"to\": 13027}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 13047, \"to\": 13051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her performance of \\\"L'Hymne \\u00e0 l'amour\\\" closed the ceremony in stunning fashion.\", \"from\": 13054, \"to\": 13133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her performance\", \"from\": 13054, \"to\": 13069}, {\"ngram\": \"L'Hymne \\u00e0 l'amour\", \"from\": 13074, \"to\": 13091}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 13100, \"to\": 13112}, {\"ngram\": \"stunning fashion\", \"from\": 13116, \"to\": 13132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clad in magnificent white, Dion's performance drew goosebumps as she rolled back the years and her incredible voiced echoed along the Seine.\", \"from\": 13134, \"to\": 13274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13268, \"end\": 13273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0042405952705265e-27, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"magnificent white\", \"from\": 13142, \"to\": 13159}, {\"ngram\": \"Dion's performance\", \"from\": 13161, \"to\": 13179}, {\"ngram\": \"goosebumps\", \"from\": 13185, \"to\": 13195}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 13215, \"to\": 13224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A massive roar greeted the end of her performance from the spectators who braved the rain throughout the night as the Eiffel Tower sparkled around her - truly a moment worthy of a singing icon.\", \"from\": 13276, \"to\": 13469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A massive roar\", \"from\": 13276, \"to\": 13290}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 13299, \"to\": 13306}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 13310, \"to\": 13325}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectators\", \"from\": 13331, \"to\": 13345}, {\"ngram\": \"the rain\", \"from\": 13357, \"to\": 13365}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 13377, \"to\": 13386}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 13390, \"to\": 13406}, {\"ngram\": \"a singing icon\", \"from\": 13454, \"to\": 13468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A long dance break in the middle of the show encapsulated the vibe that much of the show took on: It was party time in the French capital.\", \"from\": 13471, \"to\": 13609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13594, \"end\": 13600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.995627196579294, \"rank\": 0.004362184483222859, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A long dance break\", \"from\": 13471, \"to\": 13489}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 13493, \"to\": 13503}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 13507, \"to\": 13515}, {\"ngram\": \"the vibe\", \"from\": 13529, \"to\": 13537}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 13551, \"to\": 13559}, {\"ngram\": \"party time\", \"from\": 13576, \"to\": 13586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plenty of techno and Europop music accompanied by colorful dancers wearing all sorts of rave outfits - including one singer fully painted blue singing on a bed of flowers - turned heads around the world as the French displayed their party scene.\", \"from\": 13611, \"to\": 13856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13821, \"end\": 13827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.995627196579294, \"rank\": 0.004362184483222859, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Plenty\", \"from\": 13611, \"to\": 13617}, {\"ngram\": \"techno\", \"from\": 13621, \"to\": 13627}, {\"ngram\": \"Europop music\", \"from\": 13632, \"to\": 13645}, {\"ngram\": \"colorful dancers\", \"from\": 13661, \"to\": 13677}, {\"ngram\": \"all sorts\", \"from\": 13686, \"to\": 13695}, {\"ngram\": \"rave outfits\", \"from\": 13699, \"to\": 13711}, {\"ngram\": \"one singer\", \"from\": 13724, \"to\": 13734}, {\"ngram\": \"fully painted blue singing\", \"from\": 13735, \"to\": 13761}, {\"ngram\": \"a bed\", \"from\": 13765, \"to\": 13770}, {\"ngram\": \"flowers\", \"from\": 13774, \"to\": 13781}, {\"ngram\": \"turned heads\", \"from\": 13784, \"to\": 13796}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 13804, \"to\": 13813}, {\"ngram\": \"their party scene\", \"from\": 13838, \"to\": 13855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in the ceremony, the first moment that made people stop and stare was a performance by heavy metal band Gojira and their aforementioned headless Marie Antoinettes.\", \"from\": 13858, \"to\": 14029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13970, \"end\": 13976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.845665661590475e-45, \"text\": \"Gojira\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 13869, \"to\": 13881}, {\"ngram\": \"the first moment\", \"from\": 13883, \"to\": 13899}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 13910, \"to\": 13916}, {\"ngram\": \"a performance\", \"from\": 13936, \"to\": 13949}, {\"ngram\": \"their aforementioned headless Marie Antoinettes\", \"from\": 13981, \"to\": 14028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an opening ceremony full of classic rock anthems and dance tracks, the slamming drums and driving guitar was a surprising change of pace - indeed, it was the first time a metal band had played at the Opening Ceremony - but one that left a mark.\", \"from\": 14030, \"to\": 14277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an opening ceremony\", \"from\": 14033, \"to\": 14052}, {\"ngram\": \"classic rock anthems\", \"from\": 14061, \"to\": 14081}, {\"ngram\": \"dance tracks\", \"from\": 14086, \"to\": 14098}, {\"ngram\": \"the slamming drums\", \"from\": 14100, \"to\": 14118}, {\"ngram\": \"guitar\", \"from\": 14131, \"to\": 14137}, {\"ngram\": \"a surprising change\", \"from\": 14142, \"to\": 14161}, {\"ngram\": \"pace\", \"from\": 14165, \"to\": 14169}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 14187, \"to\": 14201}, {\"ngram\": \"a metal band\", \"from\": 14202, \"to\": 14214}, {\"ngram\": \"the Opening Ceremony\", \"from\": 14229, \"to\": 14249}, {\"ngram\": \"a mark\", \"from\": 14270, \"to\": 14276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang Yuwei/Pool/AFP/Getty Images There was also a stirring performance of the host nation's national anthem \\\"La Marseillaise\\\" from the top of the Grand Palais that surely sent French spirits soaring.\", \"from\": 14279, \"to\": 14480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14457, \"end\": 14463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.995627196579294, \"rank\": 0.004362184483222859, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Getty Images\", \"from\": 14300, \"to\": 14312}, {\"ngram\": \"a stirring performance\", \"from\": 14328, \"to\": 14350}, {\"ngram\": \"the host nation's national anthem\", \"from\": 14354, \"to\": 14387}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"La Marseillaise\", \"from\": 14388, \"to\": 14404}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 14411, \"to\": 14418}, {\"ngram\": \"the Grand Palais\", \"from\": 14422, \"to\": 14438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The traditional singing of John Lennon's \\\"Imagine\\\" was accompanied by a burning piano on a stage floating in the Seine, a truly incredible moment as the lights went out along the river.\", \"from\": 14482, \"to\": 14667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14509, \"end\": 14520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.539104132899623e-15, \"text\": \"John Lennon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\"}, {\"begin\": 14595, \"end\": 14600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0042405952705265e-27, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The traditional singing\", \"from\": 14482, \"to\": 14505}, {\"ngram\": \"a burning piano\", \"from\": 14552, \"to\": 14567}, {\"ngram\": \"a stage\", \"from\": 14571, \"to\": 14578}, {\"ngram\": \"a truly incredible moment\", \"from\": 14602, \"to\": 14627}, {\"ngram\": \"the lights\", \"from\": 14631, \"to\": 14641}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 14657, \"to\": 14666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as volunteers carried nations' flags into the Trocadero, a rider on a galloping steel horse glided down the Seine with the Olympic flag serving as a cape in a one-of-a-kind Olympic moment.\", \"from\": 14669, \"to\": 14861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14781, \"end\": 14786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0042405952705265e-27, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"volunteers\", \"from\": 14676, \"to\": 14686}, {\"ngram\": \"nations' flags\", \"from\": 14695, \"to\": 14709}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trocadero\", \"from\": 14715, \"to\": 14728}, {\"ngram\": \"a rider\", \"from\": 14730, \"to\": 14737}, {\"ngram\": \"a galloping steel horse\", \"from\": 14741, \"to\": 14764}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic flag\", \"from\": 14792, \"to\": 14808}, {\"ngram\": \"a cape\", \"from\": 14820, \"to\": 14826}, {\"ngram\": \"a-kind\", \"from\": 14839, \"to\": 14845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The steel horse and rider gave way to the living versions of both, carrying the Olympic flag to be officially raised.\", \"from\": 14862, \"to\": 14979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The steel horse\", \"from\": 14862, \"to\": 14877}, {\"ngram\": \"rider\", \"from\": 14882, \"to\": 14887}, {\"ngram\": \"way\", \"from\": 14893, \"to\": 14896}, {\"ngram\": \"the living versions\", \"from\": 14900, \"to\": 14919}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic flag\", \"from\": 14938, \"to\": 14954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mohd Rasfan/AFP/Getty Images The 2024 Games promised an opening ceremony unlike any other and it delivered - including on the incredible cauldron lighting.\", \"from\": 14981, \"to\": 15137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Getty Images\", \"from\": 14997, \"to\": 15009}, {\"ngram\": \"an opening ceremony\", \"from\": 15034, \"to\": 15053}, {\"ngram\": \"the incredible cauldron lighting\", \"from\": 15103, \"to\": 15135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The torch was carried by scores of French athletes and other famous Olympians of now and yesteryear - including Zinedine Zidane, Rafael Nadal (who carried the torch on a boat down the Seine), Serena Williams (who rode next to Nadal), Carl Lewis and Tony Parker.\", \"from\": 15139, \"to\": 15400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15174, \"end\": 15180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.995627196579294, \"rank\": 0.004362184483222859, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 15251, \"e